ZH: 我家的后面有一个漂亮的花园。
EN: There is a beautiful garden behind my house.

ZH: 他站在我后面。
EN: He is standing behind me.

ZH: 后面的那个房子很大。
EN: The house behind is very big.

ZH: 我的车停在停车场的后面。
EN: My car is parked behind the parking lot.

ZH: 她走在我后面。
EN: She is walking behind me.

ZH: 后面是一片开阔的草地。
EN: Behind is a vast grassland.

ZH: 书架是在我的床后面。
EN: The bookshelf is behind my bed.

ZH: 后面是一片清澈的湖水。
EN: Behind is a clear lake water.

ZH: 昨天我迷了路，结果一直跑到了马路的后面。
EN: I got lost yesterday and ended up running to the back of the road.

ZH: 公园的后面有一家小的咖啡馆。
EN: There is a small café behind the park.

ZH: 我后面坐着一个外国人。
EN: There is a foreigner sitting behind me.

ZH: 我看不清楚后面发生了什么。
EN: I can't see what happened behind.

ZH: 在后面找不到一个空位。
EN: Can't find an empty seat at the back.

ZH: 妈妈站在车站的后面等我。
EN: Mom is waiting for me behind the station.

ZH: 我喜欢坐在车厢的后面。
EN: I like to sit at the back of the carriage.

ZH: 长城的后面是一望无际的山脉。
EN: Behind the Great Wall is an endless mountain range.

ZH: 被人忽略的事实就在后面。
EN: The overlooked fact is just behind.

ZH: 在这片丛林的后面是一条小溪。
EN: Behind this forest is a small stream.

ZH: 她刚走进教室的后面就迷路了。
EN: She got lost just behind the classroom.

ZH: 这幢楼的后面有一个漂亮的花园。
EN: There is a beautiful garden behind this building.
